  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/8c13fe8d7fbb671e7f3497e860d0e4dc.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 weeks ago, the Inquisition court sentenced Alice Kyteler to be burned at the stake, on suspicion of witchcraft and participation in the coven, but she managed to escape, on the way to the place of execution<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/46fe5a8b8eeff0efb97f732e545db93f.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She hid in the forests of Blackwood and is probably still hiding there, until now <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/c3eb3340d36dfe2cdce07e170d8fea65.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span>As news arrives that residents of nearby villages are noticing strange phenomena in the forest and cases of missing childrenAnd livestock have become more frequent,<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/5160e5b284f3ae16c47c86b7a44a1b32.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to take on the role of a mercenary of the Inquisition, go to the dark forest of Blackwood and fulfill the terms of the contract to find Alice Kyteler and enforce the sentence.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/9b6b0379b500be26b2476f7745da2e6f.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to explore this gloomy and dark world, collect information, study various magical rituals, find new chemicals, and decipher the riddles and exterminate the wickedness that inhabited the Blackwood Forest in various ways.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/a2757fc76072087631b622151791f407.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/d13b945bf41b0444bab23d88ae0cee99.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/502510192e8b03abeb9ab4016f03e5e5.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>About the developers of the project - “Chase”:</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Artflux - is an independent two-person game development team based in Bishkek, and this is our first experience in developing our own game and our debut project called “Chase”.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/0fbcd9b54adcf2fc459d1a08497aca33.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/8c13fe8d7fbb671e7f3497e860d0e4dc.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 weeks ago, the Inquisition court sentenced Alice Kyteler to be burned at the stake, on suspicion of witchcraft and participation in the coven, but she managed to escape, on the way to the place of execution<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/46fe5a8b8eeff0efb97f732e545db93f.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She hid in the forests of Blackwood and is probably still hiding there, until now <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/c3eb3340d36dfe2cdce07e170d8fea65.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span>As news arrives that residents of nearby villages are noticing strange phenomena in the forest and cases of missing childrenAnd livestock have become more frequent,<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/5160e5b284f3ae16c47c86b7a44a1b32.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to take on the role of a mercenary of the Inquisition, go to the dark forest of Blackwood and fulfill the terms of the contract to find Alice Kyteler and enforce the sentence.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/9b6b0379b500be26b2476f7745da2e6f.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to explore this gloomy and dark world, collect information, study various magical rituals, find new chemicals, and decipher the riddles and exterminate the wickedness that inhabited the Blackwood Forest in various ways.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/a2757fc76072087631b622151791f407.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/d13b945bf41b0444bab23d88ae0cee99.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/502510192e8b03abeb9ab4016f03e5e5.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>About the developers of the project - “Chase”:</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Artflux - is an independent two-person game development team based in Bishkek, and this is our first experience in developing our own game and our debut project called “Chase”.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449720/extras/0fbcd9b54adcf2fc459d1a08497aca33.avif?t=1764348842\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
